<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٤٥٤⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>يغسل <span class="c2">(الرجل)</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> في <span class="c2">(الفضاء)</span> <span class="c2">(٢)</span> وكره أن يغسل الميت كذلك.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
